author: Lisa Ryan
title: Students Given Math Problem About Sexual Assault at Pennsylvania High School
text:
Ah, high school. A time for reading, parties at Kyle’s house, and of course, inappropriate math questions. At least, that’s what happened at a high school in Pennsylvania, when students were asked to solve an equation about a girl who was sexually assaulted by a family member.
